171
00:12:27,669 --> 00:12:28,836
"Shut up."

172
00:12:29,671 --> 00:12:30,922
Good.

173
00:12:31,964 --> 00:12:35,092
How old were you when you got blinded?

174
00:12:35,176 --> 00:12:37,053
- Nine.
- Nine?

175
00:12:38,054 --> 00:12:42,016
So you had nine whole
years of looking at movies,

176
00:12:42,099 --> 00:12:45,853
blue skies, up girlies'
skirts that I never had.

177
00:12:45,937 --> 00:12:48,564
I was born blind.

178
00:12:48,647 --> 00:12:51,025
You don't hear me whining about it, do you?

179
00:12:51,108 --> 00:12:52,151
No.

180
00:12:52,234 --> 00:12:57,656
So, you're nine years old, walking
along, minding your own business

181
00:12:57,740 --> 00:12:59,909
and whammo!

182
00:12:59,992 --> 00:13:03,495
Get hit by a truck,
killed dead on the spot.

183
00:13:03,579 --> 00:13:04,997
I wasn't killed.

184
00:13:05,081 --> 00:13:06,415
You lived?

185
00:13:06,498 --> 00:13:08,167
Praise God, it's a miracle.

186
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:11,170
So you survive the truck

187
00:13:11,253 --> 00:13:14,673
and get this chemical shit in your eyes.

188
00:13:14,757 --> 00:13:15,800
What next?

189
00:13:15,883 --> 00:13:17,634
I hear things.

190
00:13:17,719 --> 00:13:19,345
What kind of things?

191
00:13:19,428 --> 00:13:20,471
Everything.

192
00:13:20,554 --> 00:13:24,100
Coughs and fights and cats meowing.

193
00:13:24,183 --> 00:13:26,018
Sometimes blocks away.

194
00:13:26,102 --> 00:13:27,144
I can sense things.

195
00:13:27,228 --> 00:13:29,688
I know where things are and when they move.

196
00:13:31,148 --> 00:13:32,191
But I can't see.

197
00:13:32,274 --> 00:13:35,444
You know what they call stuff like that?

198
00:13:35,527 --> 00:13:36,653
Gifts.

199
00:13:36,738 --> 00:13:39,365
The special kind.

200
00:13:39,448 --> 00:13:42,451
The kind that very few people have.

201
00:13:43,369 --> 00:13:44,703
Or deserve.

202
00:13:44,787 --> 00:13:46,413
I never thought of it that way.

203
00:13:46,497 --> 00:13:48,457
Well, that's because you're stupid.

204
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:50,084
I'm not stupid, I'm smart.

205
00:13:50,167 --> 00:13:51,668
Because you taught yourself

206
00:13:51,753 --> 00:13:55,464
